Note:
This tool is made for converting old BCB     based maps into the new terrain system for BCB tamplate v2.0                      


Read the Notepad for the instructions.    
 

This tool map is made by [BCS]Phubar

You must use this to create a new map using the Terrain Generator first, you cannot import this save.

0.title: Rules
0.body:
CONVERTING THE MAP:

Step1 (choose either option, they are equivalent)

A- Go to http://bcb-map-cropper.rf.gd/ , paste the url of the old mat and cick “Crop”. Wait for the new page to be loaded

B- Copy the url of the old mat image, download the image and crop the gaming mat with an image editor. 


Common part- Save the cropped image and upload it on the internet (Steam could be a good idea).
Now you have the mat background for the new terrain.

In case you forgot to copy the url before converting (next steps), the service tool will have stored it for you.


Step2  (choose either option, they are equivalent)

A- Open this map, then make an addidtive load of the map that you want to convert. 

B- Save the green pyramid tool in your saved objects, open the map that you want to convert and then import the tool. The position of the tool is not important.

Step3

Click the “Convert” button and save the map in a save file. Now you have the terrain features for the new terrain.

Step4

Open the new BCB Terrain Builder map, make and additive load of your terrain, open the table controls and apply the url of the gaming mat that you uploaded afrer cropping it.
Click the “Export” button and confirm.

Congratulations, you have your new terrain ready for playing!

Step5

Save the terrain in a save file and upload it to the workshop if you want.
